    "subtype": "equipment",
    "text": "This snare is designed to divert a target's movement towards another snare or hazard. You may choose to have the target attempt a Will saving throw instead of a Reflex saving throw; if you do, add the fear and mental traits plus add either the visual or auditory trait.  \n When a Small or larger creature enters the square, the snare Pushes the creature 5 feet and the target becomes clumsy 1 until the end of their next turn. On a critical failure the snare Pushes the target 10 feet and the target becomes clumsy 2 until the end of their next turn.",
